<section>
    <h2>Apply Here!</h2>
    <p>
        If you're motivated by our mission, excited to push boundaries, and believe your skills and mindset align with our team, we'd love to hear from you! 
        We are always looking for passionate, proactive, and committed individuals who want to grow, learn, and make an impact.
    </p>
    <p>
        If this sounds like you, please complete the following form to apply:
        <a href="https://forms.gle/UYRq6gvztvvMftTC6">Application Form</a>
    </p>
    <p>
        If you have any questions or would like to know more before applying, feel free to reach out to us at 
        <a href="mailto:cvar.upm.racing@gmail.com">cvar.upm.racing@gmail.com</a> 
        or contact us directly. We’ll be happy to help!
    </p>
    <p>
        You are also welcome to visit us in person to learn more about our work, meet the team, and see our projects firsthand. 
        We are located at the Centro de Automática y Robótica (CVAR), which is part of the Universidad Politécnica de Madrid (UPM) and the Spanish National Research Council (CSIC).
        You can find us at the following address:
        <br>
        <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/PUqYYYRRsRw5wdjp6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer ">
            Centro de Automática y Robótica (CVAR) - UPM-CSIC
            <br>
            C. de José Gutiérrez Abascal, Chamartín, 28006 Madrid, Spain
        </a>
    </p>
